# INTERNAL DOCS -- this repo is PUBLIC. Candid internal material (audits, stress
# tests, accelerator application drafts, reviews of Clay's work) lives in the
# PRIVATE `bower-docs` repo, mirrored from ~/restless-egg/docs. Never commit it here.
#
# THE RULES BELOW PROTECT BY FILENAME PREFIX, AND THAT IS NOT ENOUGH. A doc is
# candid because of what it SAYS, not what it is called, so a new candid doc
# under any other name is unprotected by default. This is not hypothetical:
# 2026-07-17-redlining-direction.md quoted brief-for-evaluators.md and stated
# the placeholder-rate / ~6x pricing gap outright, matched none of these
# patterns, and sat untracked-but-committable on a branch about to be pushed.
# It now lives in bower-docs/handoffs/.
#
# So: put candid material in docs/private/ (ignored wholesale, below), and mirror
# it to bower-docs. Do not rely on inventing a matching filename.
docs/private/
docs/audit-*
docs/stress-test-*
docs/re-application-*
docs/pr-*-review-*
docs/handoff-clay-*
docs/brief-for-evaluators.md
qa-*.mjs
docs/**/*-redlining-direction.md

# QA screenshot review artifacts (large PNGs; regenerate with npm run qa:matrix)
qa/shots/
